<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٧٠٤ - حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ مَسْلَمَةَ، عَنْ مَالِكٍ، عَنْ أَبِي حَازِمِ بْنِ دِينَارٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ سَهْلِ بْنِ سَعْدٍ السَّاعِدِيِّ <span class="special">﵁</span>:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">أَنّ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(إِنْ كَانَ فِي شَيْءٍ: فَفِي الْمَرْأَةِ، وَالْفَرَسِ وَالْمَسْكَنِ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٤٨٠٧]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
